  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-11-20T15:01:11.022543+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"s14l1\" class=\"drop-cap\">We’ve given Nano Banana a massive upgrade. Built on Gemini 3, Nano Banana Pro is our most advanced image model to date, ready to bridge the gap between imagination and professional execution.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"dep9f\">Available now in the Gemini app and starting to roll out in AI Studio, Vertex and more, it features state-of-the-art text rendering in over multiple languages, and advanced controls like the ability to input up to 14 images into a composition (varies by surface).</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"1pps2\">To get started with this powerful new model, check out our <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/nano-banana-pro\">launch post</a> and this guide below on crafting effective professional prompts.</p>\n     <hr>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5gr4l\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"s14l1\">Establishing the vision: Story, subject and style</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5l62m\">To achieve the best results and have more nuanced creative control, include the following elements in your prompt:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1pgks\"><b>Subject:</b> Who or what is in the image? Be specific. (e.g., a stoic robot barista with glowing blue optics; a fluffy calico cat wearing a tiny wizard hat).</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"f7o4b\"><b>Composition:</b> How is the shot framed? (e.g., extreme close-up, wide shot, low angle shot, portrait).</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1g2et\"><b>Action:</b> What is happening? (e.g., brewing a cup of coffee, casting a magical spell, mid-stride running through a field).</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"8negq\"><b>Location:</b> Where does the scene take place? (e.g., a futuristic cafe on Mars, a cluttered alchemist's library, a sun-drenched meadow at golden hour).</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"c9cns\"><b>Style:</b> What is the overall aesthetic? (e.g., 3D animation, film noir, watercolor painting, photorealistic, 1990s product photography).</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"f6oh3\"><b>Editing Instructions:</b> For modifying an existing image, be direct and specific. (e.g., change the man's tie to green, remove the car in the background)</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"s14l1\">Refining the details: Camera, lighting and format</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"ekujj\">While simple prompts still work, achieving professional results requires more specific instructions. When crafting your prompts, move beyond the basics and consider these advanced elements:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"atmbi\"><b>Composition and aspect ratio:</b> Define the canvas. (e.g., \"A 9:16 vertical poster,\" \"A cinematic 21:9 wide shot.\")</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"39ji0\"><b>Camera and lighting details:</b> Direct the shot like a cinematographer. (e.g., \"A low-angle shot with a shallow depth of field (f/1.8),\" \"Golden hour backlighting creating long shadows,\" \"Cinematic color grading with muted teal tones.\")</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"eguog\"><b>Specific text integration:</b> Clearly state what text should appear and how it should look. (e.g., \"The headline 'URBAN EXPLORER' rendered in bold, white, sans-serif font at the top.\")</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"3ll69\"><b>Factual constraints (for diagrams):</b> Specify the need for accuracy and ensure your inputs themselves are factual (e.g., \"A scientifically accurate cross-section diagram,\" \"Ensure historical accuracy for the Victorian era.\").</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1jf5d\"><b>Reference inputs:</b> When using uploaded images, clearly define the role of each. (e.g., \"Use Image A for the character's pose, Image B for the art style, and Image C for the background environment.\")</li>\n     </ul>\n     <hr>\n     <p data-block-key=\"62loa\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"s14l1\">Prompting examples: A showcase of creative techniques</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"do7n\">Different prompting strategies can help you craft everything from photorealistic edits to fantastical new worlds. Here are some techniques to try:</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"e9nhe\"><b>1. Generate visuals with incredible text rendering:</b> Sharp, legible text helps you create impactful posters, intricate diagrams, and even detailed product mockups.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6dntd\"><b>2. Create with real-world knowledge:</b> Built on <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/gemini-3/\">Gemini 3 Pro</a>, Nano Banana uses Gemini 3’s real-world knowledge and deep reasoning capabilities to deliver precise, detailed, rich image results.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"aduea\"><b>3. Translate and localize your ideas:</b> Generate localized text, or translate text inside images. See what products might look like in <a href=\"http://deepmind.google/models/gemini-image/pro\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">multiple languages</a>, ready for international markets, and create posters and infographics for use across different regions.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Astronaut.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Astronaut.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;storyboard about an astronaut&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Text_Rendering_2.max-768x768.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Text_Rendering_2.max-1408x768.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Woodchuck AI generation&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/World_Knowledge_Elaichi_Chai.max-768x768.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/World_Knowledge_Elaichi_Chai.max-1408x768.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Chai making infographic&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/NanoBanana_TranslateCans_8COQ.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/NanoBanana_TranslateCans_8COQ.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Yellow cans translated to Korean&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1763652922950\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 351.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 4\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Astronaut.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Astronaut.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"storyboard about an astronaut\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Astronaut.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"70h31\">Caption: A black and white storyboard sketch showing an establishing shot, medium shot, close-up, and POV shot for a film scene.</p>\n           <p data-block-key=\"3dhab\">Prompt: Create a storyboard for this scene</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"5cwb8\"><b>4. Use studio-quality control edits:</b> Get extensive controls for professional-grade results. Directly influence lighting and camera settings like angle, focus, color grading and more.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"kri7\"><b>5. Resize with precision:</b> Experiment with different aspect ratios and generate crisp visuals at 1K, 2K or 4K resolution across various products.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9ffa7\"><b>6. Blend images and keep multiple characters consistent:</b> Maintain the consistency and resemblance of multiple characters, even when they appear together in a group. Take up to 6 to 14 (input number varies by surface) entirely unconnected images and blend them to create something new.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"boghm\"><b>7. Create and maintain your brand look and feel:</b> Render and apply designs with consistent brand styling to visualize concepts easily. Seamlessly drape patterns, logos, and artwork onto 3D objects and surfaces—from apparel to packaging—while preserving natural lighting and texture.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Fox.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Fox.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;Fox in the daytime and at night&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM---Flower-Girl.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM---Flower-Girl.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A girl in focus and then flowers in focus&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Aspect-Ratio.max-1226x1226.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Aspect-Ratio.max-1226x1226.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A person with feathers around him in various aspect ratios&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Multi-Asset-Fashion.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Multi-Asset-Fashion.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A fashion image composite made up of various elements&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/nanowave.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/nanowave.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A logo input that leads to various applications in design thanks to Nano Banana Pro&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;\n      }\n    \n  ]\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"article-module ga4-carousel\" data-component=\"uni-image-carousel\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Article Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;}\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"article-carousel\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\">\n     <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"carousel-item-1763652922950\" data-slider-height-loaded=\"true\" style=\"height: 831.875px;\">\n      <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide article-carousel__slide--active\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 5\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Fox.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Fox.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"Fox in the daytime and at night\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/WM-Fox.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"hytej\">Prompt: Turn this scene into nighttime</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$365059525$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1763652922950-4\" data-index=\"5\"><!--?lit$365059525$-->Jump to position 5</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;7 tips to get the most out of Nano Banana Pro&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"5cwb8\">A note on current limitations</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2hn3f\">As we continue to develop and fine-tune our models, there are still areas in need of improvement:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"88ife\"><b>Visual and text fidelity:</b> Rendering small text, fine details, and producing accurate spellings may not work perfectly.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"cvhnu\"><b>Data and factual accuracy:</b> Always verify the factual accuracy of data-driven visuals like diagrams and infographics.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ao1tv\"><b>Translation and localization:</b> Multilingual text generation may make grammar mistakes or miss specific cultural nuances.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"7n9sk\"><b>Complex edits and image blending:</b> Advanced editing tasks like blending or lighting changes can sometimes produce unnatural artifacts.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"cl2mg\"><b>Character features:</b> While usually reliable, character consistency across edits may vary.</li>\n     </ul>\n     <p data-block-key=\"4v4kp\">We’re actively working to improve these areas and appreciate your creativity as we build the next generation of image tools together.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-related-content-tout title=\"Introducing Nano Banana Pro\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"Nano Banana Pro is our new image generation and editing model from Google DeepMind.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Related Article\" image-alt-text=\"\" role=\"none\" fullurl=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/nano-banana-pro/\" pagetype=\"articlepage\" isarticlepage=\"\" data-ga4-related-article=\"{\n  &quot;event&quot;: &quot;article_lead_click&quot;,\n  &quot;link_text&quot;: &quot;Introducing Nano Banana Pro&quot;,\n  &quot;link_type&quot;: &quot;internal&quot;,\n  &quot;full_url&quot;: &quot;https://blog.google/technology/ai/nano-banana-pro/&quot;,\n  &quot;title&quot;: &quot;Introducing Nano Banana Pro&quot;,\n  &quot;author&quot; : &quot;Naina Raisinghani&quot;,\n  &quot;slug&quot;: &quot;nano-banana-pro&quot;,\n  &quot;position&quot;: &quot;1 of 1&quot;,\n  &quot;click_location&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;,\n  &quot;primary_tag&quot;: &quot;Topics - AI&quot;,\n  &quot;secondary_tags&quot;: &quot;Gemini Models,Gemini App,Search&quot;,\n  &quot;published_date&quot;: &quot;2025-11-20|15:00&quot;,\n  &quot;hero_media_type&quot;: &quot;video&quot;,\n  &quot;days_since_published&quot;: &quot;0&quot;,\n  &quot;content_category&quot;: &quot;Announcement&quot;,\n  &quot;word_count&quot;: &quot;902&quot;,\n  &quot;has_audio&quot;: &quot;no&quot;,\n  &quot;has_video&quot;: &quot;yes&quot;,\n  &quot;has_image&quot;: &quot;yes&quot;,\n  &quot;has_carousel&quot;: &quot;yes&quot;\n}\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"none\" class=\" related-content-tout related-content-tout--max-width uni-component-spacing \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Related Content Tout&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Introducing Nano Banana Pro&quot;}\">\n    <a class=\"related-content-tout__wrapper\" href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/nano-banana-pro/\" aria-label=\"\n      Related Article.\n       Introducing Nano Banana Pro.\n      Nano Banana Pro is our new image generation and editing model from Google DeepMind. See more\"><!--?lit$365059525$--></a>\n   </section>\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文提供 7 个技巧和高级提示技术，旨在帮助用户最大限度地发挥谷歌 Nano Banana Pro 图像生成模型的创意和专业能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文提供 7 个技巧和高级提示技术，旨在帮助用户最大限度地发挥谷歌 Nano Banana Pro 图像生成模型的创意和专业能力。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了 Nano Banana Pro，谷歌基于 Gemini 3 构建的先进图像模型，重点介绍了其卓越的文本渲染能力和精细化控制选项。然后，它提供了一个全面的指南，包含七个关键技巧，用于编写有效的提示语，以获得专业级的图像生成效果。这些技巧包括建立清晰的图像要素（主题、构图、动作、地点、风格）和细化细节（相机设置、光照、宽高比、特定文本集成、事实约束和参考输入）。本文展示了各种创意技术，如生成具有令人难以置信的文本渲染效果的视觉效果，利用真实世界的知识，翻译想法，使用工作室质量的控制，精确调整大小，混合图像，并保持角色的一致性，以及维护品牌形象。它还透明地解决了当前的局限性，如小字体文本的清晰度和复杂编辑的问题，并承认正在进行的开发。",
